Question:
Let \[f(x) = \left\{
\begin{array}{cl} ax+3, &\text{ if }x>2, \\
x-5 &\text{ if } -2 \le x \le 2, \\
2x-b &\text{ if } x <-2, \text{ and also if } x = 5.
\end{array}
\right.\]Find $a+b$ if the piecewise function is continuous.

